@startuml ZhangZhishuoDetail
title 张致硕 zhangzhishuo：蜂巢管理与文件上传完整类关系

top to bottom direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontName Microsoft YaHei
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam nodesep 55
skinparam ranksep 55
hide empty members
hide circle

skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor<<Controller>> #E8F3FF
  BackgroundColor<<Service>> #EAF7EA
  BackgroundColor<<Mapper>> #FFF4D8
  BackgroundColor<<Entity>> #F7F7F7
  BackgroundColor<<DTO>> #F4EAFE
  BackgroundColor<<Common>> #FDEEEE
  BackgroundColor<<Utility>> #F2F2F2
  BackgroundColor<<External>> #FFFFFF
}

legend right
  张致硕负责：蜂巢创建和维护、成员管理、邀请加入、文件上传、统一响应和异常处理。
  实线表示直接调用或构造器依赖，虚线表示 DTO、事件、注解或轻量使用。
endlegend

package "张致硕负责包 com.hive.zhangzhishuo" as ZZS #E8F3FF {
  class "ApiResponse<T>（统一响应）" as ApiResponse <<DTO>>
  class "BizException（业务异常）" as BizException <<Common>>
  class "GlobalExceptionHandler（异常处理）" as GlobalExceptionHandler <<Common>>
  class "Ids（邀请码工具）" as Ids <<Utility>>
  class "DemoDataSeeder（演示数据）" as DemoDataSeeder <<Utility>>

  class "HiveController（蜂巢接口）" as HiveController <<Controller>>
  class "InviteController（邀请接口）" as InviteController <<Controller>>
  class "FileController（文件上传接口）" as FileController <<Controller>>

  class "HiveService（蜂巢业务）" as HiveService <<Service>>

  interface "HiveMapper（蜂巢表）" as HiveMapper <<Mapper>>
  interface "HiveMemberMapper（蜂巢成员表）" as HiveMemberMapper <<Mapper>>
  interface "InviteMapper（邀请表）" as InviteMapper <<Mapper>>
  interface "FileMapper（文件表）" as FileMapper <<Mapper>>

  class "Hive（蜂巢实体）" as Hive <<Entity>>
  class "HiveMember（蜂巢成员实体）" as HiveMember <<Entity>>
  class "Invite（邀请实体）" as Invite <<Entity>>
  class "StoredFile（文件实体）" as StoredFile <<Entity>>

  class "HiveReq（蜂巢请求）" as HiveReq <<DTO>>
  class "HiveVO（蜂巢响应）" as HiveVO <<DTO>>
  class "HiveDetailVO（蜂巢详情）" as HiveDetailVO <<DTO>>
  class "MemberVO（成员响应）" as MemberVO <<DTO>>
  class "CreateInviteReq（创建邀请请求）" as CreateInviteReq <<DTO>>
  class "InviteVO（邀请响应）" as InviteVO <<DTO>>
  class "MuteReq（禁言请求）" as MuteReq <<DTO>>
}

package "外部依赖：张凯文 zhangkaiwen" as ZKW_EXT #EAF7EA {
  class ChannelService <<External>>
  class MessageService <<External>>
  class WsPush <<External>>
  interface ChannelMapper <<External>>
  interface MessageMapper <<External>>
  class Channel <<External>>
  class CreateChannelReq <<External>>
  class ChannelVO <<External>>
  class UnreadRow <<External>>
}

package "外部依赖：虞沛远 yupeiyuan" as YPY_EXT #FFF4D8 {
  class PermissionService <<External>>
  class Permissions <<External>>
  interface RoleMapper <<External>>
  interface MemberRoleMapper <<External>>
  class MemberRole <<External>>
  class Role <<External>>
  class RoleVO <<External>>
}

package "外部依赖：江民智 jiangminzhi" as JMZ_EXT #F4EAFE {
  annotation CurrentUid
  interface UserMapper <<External>>
  class User <<External>>
  class "AppEvents.HiveCreated" as HiveCreatedEvent <<External>>
}

GlobalExceptionHandler ..> ApiResponse : 统一错误响应
GlobalExceptionHandler ..> BizException : 捕获业务异常

HiveController ..> ApiResponse
InviteController ..> ApiResponse
FileController ..> ApiResponse
HiveController --> HiveService : 蜂巢和成员接口
InviteController --> HiveService : 邀请码加入
FileController --> FileMapper : 保存上传元数据

HiveController ..> CurrentUid
InviteController ..> CurrentUid
FileController ..> CurrentUid
HiveController ..> HiveReq
HiveController ..> MuteReq
HiveController ..> CreateInviteReq

HiveService --> HiveMapper : 蜂巢持久化
HiveService --> HiveMemberMapper : 成员持久化
HiveService --> InviteMapper : 邀请码持久化
HiveService --> ChannelMapper : 默认频道
HiveService --> MessageMapper : 消息清理和统计
HiveService --> RoleMapper : 默认角色
HiveService --> MemberRoleMapper : 成员角色
HiveService --> UserMapper : 用户查询
HiveService --> PermissionService : 权限校验
HiveService --> MessageService : 系统消息
HiveService --> WsPush : 变更推送
HiveService ..> HiveCreatedEvent : 发布事件
HiveService ..> Permissions : 权限位
HiveService ..> HiveDetailVO
HiveService ..> HiveVO
HiveService ..> MemberVO
HiveService ..> InviteVO
HiveService ..> Ids : 生成邀请码
HiveService ..> Channel
HiveService ..> ChannelVO
HiveService ..> Role
HiveService ..> RoleVO
HiveService ..> MemberRole
HiveService ..> UnreadRow

DemoDataSeeder --> UserMapper : 初始化用户
DemoDataSeeder --> HiveMemberMapper : 初始化成员
DemoDataSeeder --> HiveService : 初始化蜂巢
DemoDataSeeder --> ChannelService : 初始化频道
DemoDataSeeder --> MessageService : 初始化消息
DemoDataSeeder ..> User
DemoDataSeeder ..> Channel
DemoDataSeeder ..> CreateChannelReq
DemoDataSeeder ..> ChannelVO

HiveMapper ..> Hive
HiveMemberMapper ..> HiveMember
HiveMemberMapper ..> MemberVO
InviteMapper ..> Invite
InviteMapper ..> InviteVO
FileMapper ..> StoredFile
HiveDetailVO ..> ChannelVO
HiveDetailVO ..> RoleVO
HiveDetailVO ..> UnreadRow

@enduml
